  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;In the event that the solar PV and solar thermal equipment hereby approved is no longer in operational use, all equipment shall be removed from the roof within six months of it ceasing to function and the building fabric made good, using the original building fabric removed to facilitate the development.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To preserve the historic fabric of the Designated Heritage asset.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The development hereby permitted must be begun not later than the expiration of three years beginning with the date of this permission.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: In order to comply with the provisions of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990 (as amended).&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The Development hereby permitted shall only be carried out and completed strictly in accordance with the submitted plans hereby approved and any subsequent approval of details.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To ensure that the development hereby permitted is carried out in full accordance with the plans hereby approved.&lt;/p&gt;"
